10pm to 10:30pm S45E07 Live

Joining Jools in the studio this week is English rock singer Robert Plant with his band the Sensational Space Shifters. Counting Crows return to the show for the first time since 1997. From New England, tUnE-yArDs is the moniker of Oakland-based musician Merrill Garbus, who performs a couple of tracks from her third album Nikki Nack. And two acts make their TV debuts, Gedeon Luke and the People and Years and Years. Plus south London grime artist Stormzy.
